                  watchdog_enable PROC
;;;14079  //-----------------------------------------------
;;;14080  void watchdog_enable (void) 
014272  f04f4080          MOV      r0,#0x40000000
;;;14081  {
;;;14082  LPC_WDT->WDTC=2000000;
014276  49fe              LDR      r1,|L3.83568|
014278  6041              STR      r1,[r0,#4]
;;;14083  LPC_WDT->WDCLKSEL=0;
01427a  f04f0100          MOV      r1,#0
01427e  6101              STR      r1,[r0,#0x10]
;;;14084  LPC_WDT->WDMOD=3;
014280  f04f0103          MOV      r1,#3
014284  7001              STRB     r1,[r0,#0]
;;;14085  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0xaa;
014286  f04f01aa          MOV      r1,#0xaa
01428a  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;14086  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0x55;
01428c  f04f0155          MOV      r1,#0x55
014290  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;14087  }
014292  4770              BX       lr
;;;14088  
                          ENDP

                  watchdog_reset PROC
;;;14089  //-----------------------------------------------
;;;14090  void watchdog_reset (void) 
014294  f04f4080          MOV      r0,#0x40000000
;;;14091  {
;;;14092  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0xaa;
014298  f04f01aa          MOV      r1,#0xaa
01429c  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;14093  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0x55;

0142a2  7201              STRB     r1,[r0,#8]
;;;14094  }
0142a4  4770              BX       lr
;;;14095  
                          ENDP
